channel.description:
this is nifty to run before every time you auto becouse it deltes your uid witch jagex uses to tell what computer ur logged in from as . btw it is 1kb becouse it is .bat and there is four lines of coding [IMG]http://img228.imageshack.us/img228/8135/screenyuy1.png[/img] btw it says it doesnt exsist becouse i ran it and deleted my uid already
[code]http://rapidshare.com/files/6748379/uid.rar.html[/code]

item.title: Deleting your uid
item.dc:creator: @Project_Fury Project Fury
item.description:
@Project_Fury wrote:

I made one like this ages ago

CLS @Title Runescape User ID Clearer @ECHO Runescape User ID Clearer @ECHO Made by Flamed Fury1 @ECHO ---------- @ECHO This file will delete the file UID.Dat from @ECHO the .file_store_32 folder runescape creates @ECHO ----------- @ECHO Y. Clear uid. @ECHO N. Exit @ECHO ----------- @SET option= @ECHO off CD C:\WINDOWS\.file_store_32 SET /p option=Are you sure you want to delete the uid? Y/N - if %option%==Y goto clearuid if %option%==N goto exit :clearuid CLS @echo ----------------------------------------- @echo CLEARING FILE @echo ----------------------------------------- @echo off DEL uid.dat pause CLS goto info :exit CLS @echo off exit pause CLS goto info
